law.history: Repealed 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 445, sec. 14, effective July 14, 1992; and amended ch. 211, sec. 48. -- Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 497, sec. 21, effective July 13, 1990.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Property of inmates -- Preservation of evidence or contraband.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/92). This section was amended by the 1992 Regular Session of the General Assembly and also repealed. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
